data.Name: Set It Off
data.Bio: Set It Off is a band from Tampa, Florida, formed in 2008. Members include: Cody Carson (vocals, guitar), Zach Dewall (guitar, vocals) and Maxx Danziger (drums). Cody started the band after singing "Coffee Shop Soundtrack" on stage with All Time Low. Read more on Last.fm
